{"tid":1753882,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"區選大勝後 泛民如何連結勇武 同市民走下去","createTime":"2019-11-25T04:55:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T05:03:34.000Z","uid":87915,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ba687e8e7e5d191cb17f7723efba38f545873897","tid":1753882,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:55:10.000Z","msg":"先利申，我係睇咗好多唔同人嘅評論及建議作簡單整合，特別係沈旭輝，絕大部分意見唔係我諗，但我極之認同<br />\n<br />\n60% vs 40%  <br />\n我係相信呢個比例大家都出盡奶力嘅結果<br />\n<br />\n即係 雖然我地係大多數 但唔係贏到開巷。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">立 法 會 好 危 險</span></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 首先，正如杜汶澤話齋，以前投比泛民，我寧願射落海。但6月9日起，我地一寸都唔輸得，要全方位都係作戰狀態。<br />\n<br />\n2. 不割蓆 不分化。事實係有選區內鬨而輸，但不分化<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3. 最重要 連結勇武<br />\n<br />\n請區議員們 每月捐出定額人工  成立基金<br />\n基金由大家公認 嘅人運行<br />\n主要支援被捕人士 及 黃色經濟圈<br />\n詳情請睇 沈旭輝 文章    非常值得睇</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4. 功能組別<br />\n係時候要有人攻打功能組別"},{"pid":"53d8daf54aac3b2cd867cd5fc059fa608bc517b6","tid":1753882,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:55:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"13c308a27bc619be9817d609ddbe7b8b806cf917","tid":1753882,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:55:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf4169944630e7c9d9dd717e501477029f7c2330","tid":1753882,"uid":93962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:56:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"759f3aa077af85da9890ad9105db022d33cfe841","tid":1753882,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:58:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c404d09425d3ea1bb74ee126e0370d1572618ec9","tid":1753882,"uid":87915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:00:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a54b096295deebab05248b4f27d9185c37f88f3","tid":1753882,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:03:34.000Z","msg":"灣仔區議會最早何時可以通過「警察立即撤圍理大，否則決議拆除回歸紀念碑」？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢枝係風水邪陣厭勝棒！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/100o16000000zn4azC00C_Z_640_10000.jpg?proc=source%2ftrip\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdimg04.c-ctrip.com%2Fimages%2F100o16000000zn4azC00C_Z_640_10000.jpg%3Fproc%3Dsource%252ftrip&h=e701bbc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家J到15:00好啦, J完就要迫區議會做實事, 救手足啦！"}]}